- 'Binance' is a major cryptocurrency exchange platform;
- 'Individuals accessing information' implies looking up user actions related to market data retrieval.

sql:
SELECT timestamp, open, high, low, close, volume, symbol
FROM market_data
WHERE close > (SELECT AVG(close) FROM market_data);

